external_knowledge:
- Popular: Models viewed more than 5 times;
- High-Performing: Top 5 models based on the average F1 score;
- Updated Recently: Models updated within the last 30 days.

- Shining stars: Refers to top-performing models;
- Identities: Refers to the model's unique identifier and name;
- Brilliance: Represents the performance metric, specifically the F1 score;
- Quintet: Denotes the top five models.
